# Day 5 - Multiplication Table Generator

This is my Day 5 project of the 30 Days JavaScript Challenge.

##  Project Description
A simple web application that generates a multiplication table based on the number entered by the user.

##  Features
- Generate table from 1 to 10
- Dynamic output display
- Input validation (handles empty input)
- Simple and clean UI

##  Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Project Structure
index.html
style.css
script.js
## How to Use
1. Enter a number
2. Click on "Generate"
3. Multiplication table will be displayed

